text: ane ame isra'ilana santanane dariyo para karavi didho, pachi temani pachala-pachala phira'auna potana laskara sathe atyacara karavana hetuthi avyo, tyam sudhi ke jyare te dubava lagyo to kaheva lagyo ke hum imana lavum chum ke jena para isra'ilana santano imana lavya, tena sivaya ko'i pujya nathi ane hum musalamano manthi chum
